{"tid":1290811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家眼中嘅香港民族係咩?","createTime":"2019-07-06T15:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T11:13:45.000Z","uid":69753,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d4a866cf5c735840d799698ca96ec0c0d23534","tid":1290811,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"係咪「視港如家，識香港文化、廣東話」就係香港民族?<br />\n假設滿足以上條件...<br />\n蝻亞狗係咪? 白皮豬係咪? 黑鬼係咪? 東南亞人係咪?<br />\n東亞人? 「華人」? 粵人?<br />\n單非? 雙非?<br />\n<br />\n係咪所有都係香港民族?"},{"pid":"1216ff7781455faf5d15b7c6c32bfe172607c8ea","tid":1290811,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c161c2a6d58a8a4be93f877136fc68f08faca408","tid":1290811,"uid":5205,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:46:41.000Z","msg":"識香港語 +港式口音 反共 有禮貌 就係香港人"},{"pid":"8bc621152560dbb7f947fc21511d48e5b49eadd7","tid":1290811,"uid":69753,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"c161c2a6d58a8a4be93f877136fc68f08faca408","tid":1290811,"uid":5205,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:46:41.000Z","msg":"識香港語 +港式口音 反共 有禮貌 就係香港人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:50:48.000Z","msg":"唔曬理種族?"},{"pid":"562db80d5128f4cf12e0bd8874c353c4235a9493","tid":1290811,"uid":8543,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:59:03.000Z","msg":"咩種族都可以"},{"pid":"da29373eae17b82c6abc79acd40940d68f694d18","tid":1290811,"uid":45518,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:03:40.000Z","msg":"只要係現在/曾經長居香港，願意無條件,不問回報去為整個香港社會利益付出嘅人"},{"pid":"e5865624c73f873ce95735ecd723dbfcd48d9725","tid":1290811,"uid":87116,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:04:48.000Z","msg":"民族最重要嘅部分係共同經歷同想像<br />\n亦因為咁，令民族可以成為客觀、不由自主嘅身分<br />\n亦因為共同經歷想要用時間培養，令民族可以係一個半封閉嘅群體，唔係求其一隻蝻話認同香港價值就係香港民族"},{"pid":"f06e7341f439e5d1ef4165344d24b01b7939edbc","tid":1290811,"uid":1330,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:06:48.000Z","msg":"唔理咩種族<br />\n住喺香港+尊重香港文化 就係香港人"},{"pid":"a4c7dcbfad8d590600f6f1e15f04be323adab40c","tid":1290811,"uid":69753,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"即係要同班屎色人、多毛猩猩同一個種族?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12b85d94f4bd399175ebe4206a2a1faf989268e","tid":1290811,"uid":69753,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4c7dcbfad8d590600f6f1e15f04be323adab40c","tid":1290811,"uid":69753,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"即係要同班屎色人、多毛猩猩同一個種族?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:14:18.000Z","msg":"*民族"},{"pid":"b255de9b01c7834db8c8e1949f5d5be102adc459","tid":1290811,"uid":260806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:23:34.000Z","msg":"報稱通常居於香港<br />\n願意並計劃以香港作爲永久居留地<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不向中國共產黨卑躬屈膝</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不出賣香港整體利益</span></strong><br />\n嘅任何疑似人類<br />\n<br />\n都可以歸類爲香港民族。"},{"pid":"afec7bafd6be71bbb24b1b69cb2e1a64857e93a1","tid":1290811,"uid":206594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:27:18.000Z","msg":"其實現時係點都唔緊要<br />\n最緊要係有個理想形象<br />\n咁大家就會有個目標去改善自身<br />\n<br />\n例如話日本仔啲武士道精神，歐洲啲騎士精神<br />\n都係文化創作後期整出來<br />\n甚至最多香港人講嘅獅子山精神<br />\n都係首歌創作出來"},{"pid":"0fde7ef4afff0040c32d93a89ab7614aec58366d","tid":1290811,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:28:15.000Z","msg":"香港民族就係唔會蠢到同西方國家鬥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba6b67482050847dd725d5d0fc4979466e685a9","tid":1290811,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fde7ef4afff0040c32d93a89ab7614aec58366d","tid":1290811,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor