老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大是大非就一齊對住邪惡政權講屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03bf12b6cf4cda7c32c9673898b1ae2ec7d4a44","tid":1290811,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad12e27870e8658c8bb0ca97235ba881bff6b803","tid":1290811,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:01:46.000Z","msg":"國家可以係多民族國家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:08:52.000Z","msg":"即係點?<br />\n香港民族係多種族民族?"},{"pid":"8511bbdaa04bec39864fddf9d419d5a84203a5a6","tid":1290811,"uid":161195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:11:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecc25d33aa77c2f94e185aed8df2b41eac6f20bf","tid":1290811,"uid":206617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:15:13.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔洗理咩種族<br />\n尋日光復屯門都有南亞人出黎幫手，啲廣東話仲要好正<br />\n而且就算係連登巴絲，我諗都有唔少人係單非、雙非，甚到係大陸出世<br />\n但又如何？<br />\n梁天琦個背景係點？<br />\n只要有同一信念，真正愛護香港，大家都係香港人<br />\n不分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212e593580288d793252c474461c463c276d52cc","tid":1290811,"uid":49544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4c7dcbfad8d590600f6f1e15f04be323adab40c","tid":1290811,"uid":69753,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"即係要同班屎色人、多毛猩猩同一個種族?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:16:09.000Z","msg":"唔洗搞分化"},{"pid":"c3f9ed9cae0218f10dbc366039cfc8d18e202a97","tid":1290811,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7315b0e5d8ed01b1e407b8c7243dcee01735fe2","tid":1290811,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:17:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}